articles.title: Macron says Europe should not follow U.S. or Chinese policy over Taiwan - Reuters
articles.description: French President Emmanuel Macron said in comments published on Sunday that Europe had no interest in an acceleration of the crisis over Taiwan and should pursue a strategy independent of both Washington and Beijing.

articles.title: WHO warns against Aedes aegypti's presence in Europe - Prensa Latina
articles.description: Geneva, Apr 8 (Prensa Latina) The World Health Organization (WHO) has warned that the presence of the Aedes aegypti mosquito is a threat in southern Europe, where measures are being taken to prevent dengue fever, Zika, and chikungunya.
